{"tid":1151902,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企得一個廁所真係好悲哀","createTime":"2019-05-12T16:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T16:27:26.000Z","uid":149563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"803852332464a7e5820ddad4830689bca498a20d","tid":1151902,"uid":149563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"屋企有老人家 但係得一個廁所<br />\n當你想用廁所嘅時候 佢哋有時就會咁啱都想去廁所<br />\n咁無辦法啦都係要讓<br />\n跟住就要坐係廳度呆等<br />\n<br />\n最慘係有時返工<br />\n又撞正佢哋出門口飲茶嘅時候<br />\n要同啲老人家爭廁所用<br />\n所以成日都遲到邊緣<br />\n有時要特登早啲起身用咗廁所先<br />\n<br />\n有次好急屎但係都忍住返屋企先去<br />\n因為真係唔鍾意公廁開大<br />\n嗰次直頭係跑返屋企<br />\n諗住一返到屋企就爆石<br />\n點知有人霸咗個廁所<br />\n我真係就嚟開曬八門忍屎<br />\n窮撚想去廁所都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ebf57500512457e90135e87e8e316f128b5161d","tid":1151902,"uid":64457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20b39739f97e3a05c9a767cbf6953c256b4f27a0","tid":1151902,"uid":143228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T16:15:47.000Z","msg":"上次上fd 屋企, 見佢屋企有3個廁所(計埋工人廁所), 咁我就好surprise 啦, 因為我屋企得一個<br />\n點知另一個fd 話: 乜唔係正常屋企都有兩個廁所咩<br />\n我: sor lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edeb6bfca82708c707524ca37a8a3960d9a30783","tid":1151902,"uid":177004,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ebf57500512457e90135e87e8e316f128b5161d","tid":1151902,"uid":64457,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T16:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T16:24:16.000Z","msg":"廢老正仆街"},{"pid":"c1f4fd5d4e91cbadfee2d77cb81dc382e628795f","tid":1151902,"uid":82829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"20b39739f97e3a05c9a767cbf6953c256b4f27a0","tid":1151902,"uid":143228,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T16:15:47.000Z","msg":"上次上fd 屋企, 見佢屋企有3個廁所(計埋工人廁所), 咁我就好surprise 啦, 因為我屋企得一個<br />\n點知另一個fd 話: 乜唔係正常屋企都有兩個廁所咩<br />\n我: sor lo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T16:27:26.000Z","msg":"我到小學都仲覺得係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為自己同親戚嗰個都兩個廁所<br />\n後尾先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申唔係窮撚不過想買嘢要自己返pt賺錢"}]}